Class StoreOrderController

com.example.sm_project4.StoreOrderController

javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class StoreOrderController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller class for the Store Order view. Handles displaying and managing store orders. Works in conjunction with JavaFX elements defined in the associated FXML file.
